# History of Python
- Python ko **1991** mein launch kiya gaya tha aur isko **Guido van Rossum** ne banaya tha.
- Iska naam ek purane British comedy TV show ("Monty Python's Flying Circus") ke naam se pada tha.
- Isko mainly simple, clean aur fast programming ke liye banaya gaya tha.

---

# Python ke Faayde (Advantages)
- Ye baaki languages ke mukable kaafi aasaan (easy) hoti hai.
- Iske keywords aasaan hote hain.
- Ye line by line code convert karti hai to error/problem turant pata chal jati hai.
- Isme clean aur chhote syntax hote hain.
- Iska code Java ya C++ se lagbhag bahut hi chhota hota hai.
- Ye dynamically typed language hai.
- Ye zyada tar har jagah (Web, Data Science, AI, Automation) use hoti hai.

---

# IDLE aur IDEs
Python ko install karne ke baad hum IDLE ya IDE ki madad se programming kar sakte hain.

- **IDLE** (Integrated Development and Learning Environment): Ye zyadatar khali learning (seekhne) purpose ke liye use hota hai.
- **IDE** (Integrated Development Environment): Ye professional aur development purpose ke liye hota hai. Market mein aisi bohot si IDEs available hain.
  - Python ki ek bohot famous IDE **PyCharm** hai, but iske advanced tools paid (paise lagte hain) hote hain.
  - Isliye development ke liye log **VS Code**, **Anaconda**, ya ab aaj ki new aur most popular IDE **Antigravity** ka use karte hain.

